tile.smart_pump.name=Smart Pump
tile.smart_pump.waila.working=Working on: %s
tile.smart_pump.waila.finished=Finished draining
nei.infopage.uie.smart_pump.1=The Smart Pump is a lag-light way to gather in-world fluids. Placed directly above the a fluid block and fed RF, it begins collecting fluid and replacing it with stone without triggering block updates.
nei.infopage.uie.smart_pump.2=Before pumping, it tries to output fluid to tanks located directly above it. The pump works chunk-wise in a diamond with a radius of 5 chunks. During operation, the pump keeps its own chunk loaded as well as the current working chunk.

