nei.infopage.uie.wood_spike.1=These spikes damage anything that walks on them, but do not kill them, instead leaving them at the minimum health possible.
nei.infopage.uie.iron_spike.1=Iron spikes kill enemies that walk on them, dropping only their non-"player-only" loot.
