nei.infopage.uie.void_quarry.1=The Void Quarry allows you to mine and harvest a large area, replacing blocks with cobblestone. It requires energy to run and outputs items to its top face. During operation, the quarry keeps its own chunk loaded as well as the current working chunk.
nei.infopage.uie.void_quarry.2=Void markers define an area for the Void Quarry to mine. Right clicking switches between three different border configuration modes. Once the border is configured, right click the Void Quarry to begin operation.
nei.infopage.uie.void_quarry.3=Once a Void Quarry is finished working, it can be restarted using the same area with a redstone signal. It also reports its progress as a signal to redstone comparators.
nei.infopage.uie.void_marker.1=Void Markers are used to define the work area of the Void Quarry. They have 3 different modes, which can be cycled through by right-clicking the marker. The first mode (standard) lets you define a rectangular area by placing 2 additional markers at 2 corners adjacent to the origin marker.
nei.infopage.uie.void_marker.2=The second mode lets you define a simple square from just a single marker, whose edge length you can change by shift right-clicking it. The third mode lets you define almost any shape, chain a full loop of any amount of markers by placing them directly in front of one another (i.e. only 90 degree turns).
nei.infopage.uie.void_marker.3=You can also limit the upper and lower Y bounds of the work area by placing a marker at your target height below and above the Void Quarry. Otherwise, it always mines down to bedrock.
nei.infopage.uie.void_quarry_upgrade=Void Quarry upgrades can be placed next to any face of the Void Quarry to add additional abilities or improvements.
nei.infopage.uie.void_quarry_upgrade.world_hole=The World Hole upgrade cause the Void Quarry to stop replacing blocks with cobblestone.
nei.infopage.uie.void_quarry_upgrade.silk_touch=The Silk Touch upgrade allows the Void Quarry to collect drops as if it is enchanted with Silk Touch (For instance, gathers stone instead of cobblestone). 
nei.infopage.uie.void_quarry_upgrade.fluid_pump=The Fluid Pump upgrade allows the Void Quarry to collect fluids as well as blocks. Fluids are output to any tank adjacent to any face.
nei.infopage.uie.void_quarry_upgrade.speed=The Speed upgrades increase the operation speed and energy cost of the Void Quarry.
nei.infopage.uie.void_quarry_upgrade.fortune=The Fortune upgrades allow the Void Quarry to collect additional drops as if it is enchanted with Fortune at the cost of additional energy.

