nei.infopage.uie.filing_cabinet.1=Filing Cabinets provide a convenient way to store large amounts of items, with some restrictions. The standard cabinet can only hold items of the same type, but with different metadata/NBT.
nei.infopage.uie.filing_cabinet.2=The Advanced Filing Cabinet can only hold items that do not normally stack, but has no type restrictions and more unique item slots.
nei.infopage.uie.filing_cabinet.3=The Elite Filing Cabinet has no restrictions whatsoever, but has the lowest number of unique item slots.
